                                        <p style="text-align:justify">Mỗi vi&ecirc;n n&eacute;n c&oacute; chứa:</p>

<ul>
	<li style="text-align:justify">Inositol: 25mg, calci pantothenate: 22mg (tương đương acid&nbsp;pantothenic: 20mg), vitamin B1 (thiamin mononitrate): 20mg, niacin: 20mg, vitamin B6 (pyridoxin hydroclorid): 15mg, vitamin B2 (riboflavin): 15mg, vitamin B12 (cyanocobalamin): 10&mu;g, acid folic: 100&mu;g, biotin: 25&mu;g.</li>
	<li style="text-align:justify">Phụ liệu: cellulose vi tinh thể, tinh bột, ester glycerin acid b&eacute;o, shellac vừa đủ 1 vi&ecirc;n.</li>
</ul>

